66413/|publisher=TV by the Number|date=2015-02-23|accessdate=2015-02-24|archive-date=2015-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150223234426/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/02/23/tv-ratings-sunday-oscars-telecast-down-sharply-from-2014-dateline-flat/366413/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=2015 Academy Awards Delivers Four Year Low in Metered Market Household Ratings|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/02/23/2015-academy-awards-delivers-four-year-low-in-metered-market-household-ratings/366540/|publisher=TV by the Number|date=2015-02-23|accessdate=2015-02-24|archive-date=2015-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150224010200/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/02/23/2015-academy-awards-delivers-four-year-low-in-metered-market-household-ratings/366540/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此外，节目在18至49岁年龄段观众群获得了11%的收视率，超过该年龄段观众的29%份额<ref>{{cite web|title=Sunday Final Ratings: Oscars Adjusted Up|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/02/24/sunday-final-ratings-oscars-adjusted-up/366838/|publisher=TV by the Number|date=2015-02-24|accessdate=2015-02-24|archive-date=2015-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151022064452/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/02/24/sunday-final-ratings-oscars-adjusted-up/366838/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。本届典礼是自2009年[[第81届奥斯卡金像奖|第81届奥斯卡金像奖]]以来观众最少的一届，当年的收视人数约为3630万。

